Package: nodepool
Type: Package
Title: Dynamically Distribute Tasks Between Computational Nodes
Version: 0.1.0.9999
Date: 2023-04-26
Authors@R: c(person('Ivan', 'Krylov', role = c('aut', 'cre'), email =
 'krylov.r00t@gmail.com'), person('R Core Team', role = 'cph', comment =
 'Parts of the run_node function taken from parallel:::workCommand'))
Description: The pool behaves like an ad-hoc 'parallel' cluster, but the
 nodes can leave and re-join the cluster later. A task abandoned by a
 node without completing it is reassigned to a different node.
